{"tid":228974,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（處境題）簽咗約但違約會點？","createTime":"2017-05-04T09:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T12:15:21.000Z","uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b77d112be9f756dcfb70370405c84ffb636b372","tid":228974,"uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"我返呢間公司嗰時簽咗兩年約<br />\n合約寫咗我兩年內唔做就要賠五千<br />\n我宜家返咗四個月<br />\n我想攞埋今個月人工就劈佢老味閪七日人工就走<br />\n<br />\n而我唔做嘅原因係<br />\n一有啲咩唔識就俾人屌到飛天<br />\n老屎忽玩晒 鍾意點串你點壓你點西面都得<br />\n你反駁下呢 就開個會話足你兩個鐘<br />\n而因為我呢下回應無我之前嗰四個月一貫嘅禮貌<br />\n所以所有老屎忽好團結地一齊對我更加西<br />\n叫我做嘢好似喝狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問下各位巴打如果唔賠會點？<br />\nbtw我唔係賠唔到五千 係我人工已經好低<br />\n仲要真係有做嘢 俾佢地點來點去<br />\n我唔想受完無謂氣仲要掉返轉賠錢咁解<br />\n<br />\n預先唔該晒各巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df3df3ff3d4ebd3bf74ecd58ce8030af012c92f","tid":228974,"uid":90643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:06:13.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"9e712d68d1493d8b0d5bc20645f7cdf0831cc230","tid":228974,"uid":62070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51b00a41abe22aaa1ef9743804a6349a983b9aa1","tid":228974,"uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你推</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21de8b9802ab0c8828cf425fdfebe54b7dc687b8","tid":228974,"uid":22390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:09:32.000Z","msg":"上勞工處問下 btw博炒咪仲好<br />\n又有錢賠 又可以hea做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8841db511c682b75895d02028f87dad0ae9c0c41","tid":228974,"uid":6872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答案就在問題中............</blockquote><br />\n師父 徒兒不明白呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/l